text: Muraz () is a rural locality (a village) in Imendyashevsky Selsoviet, Gafuriysky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 124 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 52 km from Krasnousolsky, 2 km from Karagayevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Gafuriysky District
title: Muraz, Republic of Bashkortostan
